//  connect the js to Html we use . we can attach the js in the html inside the body tag, inside the head tag, outside the body tag and we can connect the jsfile also by using <script stc="..."></script> etc..
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<p id="name">kajal</p>
<script> document.getElementById("name").innerHTML="My name is kajal";</script>
</body>
</html>
